Birmingham Steel sets recycling management . Birmingham Steel Corp said Monday Jim C . Nuckels has been appointed chief operating officer of Pacific Coast Recycling LLC , the company ' s southern California joint venture with Mitsui & Co Ltd . Nuckels has served Birmingham Steel in a variety of positions in administration and scrap procurement since joining the company in 1980 , it said . ( ( - - New York Newsdesk 212 859 - 1610 ) ) 
